    <h1>Content Calendar</h1>
    <p class="description">A planning tool outlining when and where content publishes across channels. Marketers who plan their content are <strong>414% more likely to report success</strong> (CoSchedule).</p>
    <div class="post-meta">
      <div class="meta-author">
        <div class="meta-avatar">AVR</div>
        <div class="meta-author-info">
          <span class="meta-author-name"><a href="/authors/akshay-vr/">Akshay VR</a></span>
