            <div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>Small teams: Google Sheets or Trello. Mid-size teams: Notion, Airtable, or Asana. Specialized: CoSchedule, Sprout Social, or Later for social-first calendars. The tool matters less than consistent use — a shared spreadsheet used weekly beats a fancy tool used once.</p></div></div>
